344
00:35:51,666 --> 00:35:55,874
I don't wanna see this anymore.

345
00:35:55,916 --> 00:35:58,874
I gotta get to work.

346
00:35:58,999 --> 00:36:01,249
I don't wanna see this anymore.

347
