Yeah, you look just like it.

400
00:39:43,582 --> 00:39:45,874
Stop being weird, you fucking dork.

401
00:39:45,874 --> 00:39:47,416
You goddamn triad boys.

402
00:39:47,499 --> 00:39:49,041
I'll kick your fucking asses.

403
