508
00:46:48,916 --> 00:46:50,541
Let's start our own gang out there.

509
00:46:50,749 --> 00:46:53,207
It's tiring to be a boss.

510
00:46:53,249 --> 00:46:54,416
Dancing isn't tiring?

511
00:46:54,791 --> 00:46:55,624
Actually...

512
00:46:55,791 --> 00:46:57,624
It's easy to be happy.

513
00:46:57,624 --> 00:47:00,499
Just gotta have fun!

514
00:47:00,707 --> 00:47:02,582
