546
00:50:16,124 --> 00:50:17,707
Are Chau and Cyclone friends?

547
00:50:17,916 --> 00:50:20,832
They're sworn brothers who fought together.

548
00:50:20,957 --> 00:50:22,166
When Chau went legit,

549
00:50:22,166 --> 00:50:23,624
