550
00:50:23,707 --> 00:50:25,874
Now he's the Walled City's biggest landlord.

551
00:50:29,541 --> 00:50:31,124
There's something I've wanted to ask.

552
00:50:36,041 --> 00:50:37,791
Why are the walls so damaged?

553
00:50:37,874 --> 00:50:39,166
That was a long time ago.

554
00:50:39,166 --> 00:50:40,999
You really grew up in a bubble.

555
00:50:42,124 --> 00:50:43,707
