558
00:50:48,166 --> 00:50:51,249
Then everyone wanted the cash cow for themselves.

559
00:50:51,499 --> 00:50:53,832
It was an all-out war in the underworld.

560
00:50:53,916 --> 00:50:56,082
In the end, only his boss Cyclone and

561
00:50:56,166 --> 00:50:57,999
a man named Lui were left standing.

562
00:50:58,041 --> 00:51:00,082
Lui stood a chance against my boss,

563
00:51:00,207 --> 00:51:01,749
but not because of his skills.

564
00:51:01,957 --> 00:51:04,207
It's because he had

565
00:51:04,291 --> 00:51:06,374
