569
00:51:47,874 --> 00:51:48,749
Chau!

570
00:51:48,874 --> 00:51:50,624
Help us, Chau!

571
00:51:51,624 --> 00:51:52,874
Chau!

572
00:51:55,957 --> 00:51:58,249
He even killed Chau's wife and kids...

573
00:52:06,874 --> 00:52:08,791
And took my boss's eye!

574
00:52:18,332 --> 00:52:20,082
How did Cyclone win in the end?

575
00:52:20,124 --> 00:52:22,582
The battle raged for 7 days, 7 nights.

576
00:52:22,832 --> 00:52:24,499
It was one day, one night.

577
00:52:30,916 --> 00:52:31,832
In the end...

578
00:52:32,999 --> 00:52:34,666
Cyclone killed Jim.

579
00:52:49,041 --> 00:52:50,041
Hey, we're late.

580
00:52:52,082 --> 00:52:52,707
Lok.

581
00:53:03,999 --> 00:53:05,416
What the fuck?

582
00:53:06,249 --> 00:53:08,041
Why'd you order so much?

583
00:53:08,624 --> 00:53:10,082
Won money at the tracks?

584
00:53:10,291 --> 00:53:11,916
You'll know soon.

585
00:53:19,374 --> 00:53:20,249
Boss Tiger.

586
00:53:23,541 --> 00:53:24,541
Boss Tiger.

587
00:53:28,666 --> 00:53:29,666
Hey, you're late.

588
00:53:30,666 --> 00:53:33,624
Had to deal with trouble on Temple Street.

589
00:53:33,957 --> 00:53:35,624
This meal's on me.

590
00:53:37,916 --> 00:53:38,791
What the hell's going on?

591
00:53:38,957 --> 00:53:41,416
Fuck if I know, someone's being cryptic.

592
00:53:43,624 --> 00:53:45,207
I finally found him.

593
00:53:45,791 --> 00:53:47,124
Who'd you find?

594
00:53:47,957 --> 00:53:49,291
Jim's son.

595
00:53:52,957 --> 00:53:54,374
Chrysanthemum Room.

596
00:53:54,957 --> 00:53:56,291
Thank you.

597
00:53:57,832 --> 00:53:59,291
That's crazy.

598
00:54:00,166 --> 00:54:02,916
The gods sent him back.

599
00:54:05,416 --> 00:54:07,541
He deserves to die 10 times over.

600
00:54:08,416 --> 00:54:09,291
Come on!

601
00:54:09,666 --> 00:54:11,166
Let's drink to that first.

602
00:54:11,332 --> 00:54:11,832
Cheers!

603
00:54:11,916 --> 00:54:12,999
Cheers!

604
00:54:13,207 --> 00:54:14,332
Cheers!

605
00:54:20,916 --> 00:54:21,791
Boss.

606
00:54:21,874 --> 00:54:22,791
Boss Chau, Boss Cyclone.

607
00:54:22,832 --> 00:54:23,457
Boss Cyclone.

608
00:54:23,457 --> 00:54:25,124
You're all late.

609
00:54:25,207 --> 00:54:26,332
Where are your manners?

610
00:54:26,749 --> 00:54:27,749
Sorry, but...

611
00:54:27,791 --> 00:54:29,749
We dressed up out of respect.

612
00:54:30,082 --> 00:54:31,082
Boss Chau.

613
00:54:32,082 --> 00:54:33,832
Best wishes to your health.

614
00:54:33,999 --> 00:54:35,249
Thank you.

615
00:54:37,249 --> 00:54:38,499
I've never seen him before.

616
00:54:38,791 --> 00:54:39,666
Kid.

617
00:54:40,041 --> 00:54:41,791
Greet Boss Chau and Boss Tiger.

618
00:54:42,957 --> 00:54:43,916
Boss Chau.

619
00:54:44,249 --> 00:54:45,374
Boss Tiger.

620
00:54:47,457 --> 00:54:48,749
The future of the Walled City

621
00:54:48,957 --> 00:54:51,291
lies with you kids.

622
00:54:51,832 --> 00:54:52,499
Sit.

623
00:54:53,457 --> 00:54:54,457
Eat outside.

624
00:54:54,957 --> 00:54:56,541
The adults sit here.

625
00:54:57,082 --> 00:54:58,041
Let's go outside.

626
00:54:58,291 --> 00:54:59,457
Drink up.

627
00:54:59,457 --> 00:55:00,916
No one's leaving sober tonight.

628
00:55:01,124 --> 00:55:02,249
You got it!

629
00:55:02,749 --> 00:55:04,082
Let's order.

630
00:55:18,749 --> 00:55:19,916
You weren't spotted, right?

631
00:55:20,332 --> 00:55:21,957
I'm your lab rat again?

632
00:55:21,957 --> 00:55:23,416
Take off your jacket first.

633
00:55:23,791 --> 00:55:25,749
You're great at chopping goons.

634
00:55:25,916 --> 00:55:27,291
But shaving?

635
00:55:27,791 --> 00:55:28,541
Are you for real?

636
00:55:28,541 --> 00:55:29,749
I got this!

637
00:55:29,916 --> 00:55:31,832
I asked all my pals at the pier.

638
00:55:31,832 --> 00:55:32,999
No one would come.

639
00:55:32,999 --> 00:55:34,332
You're my only real friend.

640
00:55:34,499 --> 00:55:36,249
- Lie down first.
- I change my mind.

641
00:55:36,999 --> 00:55:38,374
Lie down, man.

642
00:55:40,832 --> 00:55:42,457
It's dangerous.

643
00:55:42,499 --> 00:55:43,957
Just lie down.

644
00:55:48,416 --> 00:55:50,041
My wife's pregnant.

645
00:55:50,749 --> 00:55:51,666
Congratulations.

646
00:55:51,707 --> 00:55:53,791
You've got a bundle of joy coming.

647
00:55:54,291 --> 00:55:55,374
You can be the godfather.

648
00:55:55,416 --> 00:55:56,541
No fucking way.

649
00:55:56,707 --> 00:55:58,832
If your boss knows your kid is my godson,

650
00:55:58,916 --> 00:56:00,249
you're dead.

651
00:56:01,291 --> 00:56:02,624
Then you can have the kid.

652
00:56:04,249 --> 00:56:05,874
You're crazy, man.

653
00:56:05,957 --> 00:56:07,666
Don't move.

654
00:57:20,166 --> 00:57:22,041
I have to kill Lui.

655
00:57:24,374 --> 00:57:26,207
You'll have to kill me first.

656
00:57:33,041 --> 00:57:34,582
So, only one of us

657
00:57:34,666 --> 00:57:36,166
will make it out alive?

658
00:57:36,374 --> 00:57:37,791
What do you think?

659
00:57:52,666 --> 00:57:54,416
If we can't see...

660
00:57:55,749 --> 00:57:57,207
It'll be easier to strike.

661
00:58:01,874 --> 00:58:03,749
If I die...

662
00:58:04,707 --> 00:58:06,457
Get my wife and son out.

663
00:58:07,791 --> 00:58:09,207
If I die...

664
00:58:09,791 --> 00:58:12,207
Learn how to shave and cut hair.

665
00:58:13,207 --> 00:58:14,541
Take over my barbershop.

666
00:58:36,707 --> 00:58:38,749
The boat will take you away.

667
00:58:38,832 --> 00:58:40,249
You'll be picked up when you arrive.

668
00:59:05,249 --> 00:59:06,166
Boss.

669
00:59:06,874 --> 00:59:07,957
Watch your head.

670
00:59:12,916 --> 00:59:14,332
Keep an eye on him.

671
00:59:16,707 --> 00:59:18,166
Call everyone.

672
00:59:19,916 --> 00:59:21,624
We gotta find him.

673
00:59:24,832 --> 00:59:26,582
He's an illegal

674
00:59:27,124 --> 00:59:28,707
named Chan Lok-Kwun.

675
00:59:29,041 --> 00:59:30,332
Get a move on.

676
00:59:31,541 --> 00:59:33,249
Message for 0723?

677
00:59:33,457 --> 00:59:34,499
Password?

678
00:59:36,832 --> 00:59:39,957
Message from Twelfth Master: Lok is Jim's son.

679
00:59:40,957 --> 00:59:41,791
Say what?

680
00:59:42,249 --> 00:59:46,041
Message from Twelfth Master: Lok is Jim's son.

681
00:59:50,332 --> 00:59:52,291
Is Twelve drunk?

682
00:59:52,749 --> 00:59:55,332
He said Lok is Jim's son.

683
00:59:59,082 --> 00:59:59,707
All right,

684
00:59:59,707 --> 01:00:02,291
number two Treasure Abound is a nose ahead.

685
01:00:02,541 --> 01:00:04,832
Number five Joy of Reunion is on his tail.

686
01:00:05,124 --> 01:00:07,207
Number two!

687
01:00:07,624 --> 01:00:09,499
Number two!

688
01:00:09,707 --> 01:00:11,374
Number two!

689
01:00:15,124 --> 01:00:15,707
Number two!

690
01:00:15,707 --> 01:00:16,666
- Number two!
- Go!

691
01:00:18,541 --> 01:00:21,249
Horse no. 2 wins by a nose!

692
01:00:23,082 --> 01:00:24,582
You got lucky again!

693
01:00:24,916 --> 01:00:26,416
You've got a real charmed life.

694
01:00:26,499 --> 01:00:27,916
It's not just luck.

695
01:00:27,957 --> 01:00:29,249
I've got brains, too.

696
01:00:29,332 --> 01:00:30,916
We hit the jackpot, boss.

697
01:00:30,957 --> 01:00:32,791
Winner takes all.

698
01:00:36,666 --> 01:00:38,749
I need your help with the Walled City.

699
01:00:38,874 --> 01:00:40,666
You know I can't touch it.

700
01:00:40,749 --> 01:00:42,207
If there's nothing in it for me...

701
01:00:42,291 --> 01:00:44,082
forget it.

702
01:00:44,249 --> 01:00:45,999
Demolition comes with compensation.

703
01:00:46,041 --> 01:00:48,916
What can the government afford? 100 grand?

704
01:00:50,082 --> 01:00:51,791
A single unit isn't worth much,

705
01:00:52,082 --> 01:00:53,416
but the whole Walled City

706
01:00:53,457 --> 01:00:55,041
means hundreds of millions.

707
01:00:57,249 --> 01:00:58,666
We'll have to go inside.

708
01:00:59,666 --> 01:01:00,957
That's Cyclone's turf.

709
01:01:01,749 --> 01:01:03,499
So what it's Cyclone's?

710
01:01:03,582 --> 01:01:04,499
You scared of him?

711
01:01:08,457 --> 01:01:10,374
Boss Chau, this way.

712
01:01:22,166 --> 01:01:23,874
The usual, Boss Chau?

713
01:01:23,874 --> 01:01:24,582
Yeah.

714
01:01:24,749 --> 01:01:25,624
Boss.

715
01:01:28,582 --> 01:01:29,541
Chau.

716
01:01:31,624 --> 01:01:33,416
Mr. Big, surprised to see you

717
01:01:33,499 --> 01:01:34,666
this early in the day.

718
01:01:35,499 --> 01:01:38,207
I came to talk business with you.

719
01:01:39,041 --> 01:01:41,749
There's not much for us to discuss.

720
01:01:45,166 --> 01:01:46,374
Maybe not in the past...

721
01:01:46,791 --> 01:01:48,624
But since the Walled City's coming down...

722
01:01:48,916 --> 01:01:50,457
You're its biggest landlord.

723
01:01:50,957 --> 01:01:52,416
I'd like to work with you.

724
01:01:53,124 --> 01:01:56,041
You know that's Cyclone's turf.

725
01:01:56,582 --> 01:01:57,999
He's my sworn brother.

726
01:01:58,332 --> 01:01:58,957
What's your game?

727
01:01:58,957 --> 01:02:00,957
Sworn brother? You're kinda dumb!

728
01:02:01,582 --> 01:02:02,916
Show some respect.

729
01:02:03,041 --> 01:02:04,916
We don't speak truths in here.

730
01:02:06,207 --> 01:02:08,957
You're looking for a kid
named Chan Lok-Kwun, right?

731
01:02:09,332 --> 01:02:10,999
Yeah, so what?

732
01:02:11,541 --> 01:02:12,749
I know him.

733
01:02:21,457 --> 01:02:23,041
Didn't you tell your "brother"

734
01:02:23,166 --> 01:02:24,916
that you're looking for him?

735
01:02:25,124 --> 01:02:27,207
He's practically leeching off Cyclone

736
01:02:27,374 --> 01:02:29,249
in the Walled City.

737
01:02:30,332 --> 01:02:33,374
Everyone knows about your grudge with Jim.

738
01:02:33,582 --> 01:02:36,582
Even my boss is pissed about this.

739
01:02:36,832 --> 01:02:39,041
Your wife and kid died so tragically...

740
01:02:39,541 --> 01:02:40,999
You see him as a brother,

741
01:02:41,332 --> 01:02:43,082
but he's taking you for a fool.

742
01:03:22,332 --> 01:03:24,457
It's goddamn fate...

743
01:03:32,749 --> 01:03:33,957
We got you a boat.

744
01:03:33,999 --> 01:03:34,874
Leave now.

745
01:03:36,499 --> 01:03:38,041
What do you mean?

746
01:03:38,832 --> 01:03:40,291
You're Jim's son.

747
01:03:40,582 --> 01:03:42,666
Chau and Tiger are out for blood.

748
01:03:43,207 --> 01:03:44,999
Tiger said he wants an eye for an eye.

749
01:03:45,624 --> 01:03:46,957
We're giving you a chance to live.

750
01:03:46,999 --> 01:03:47,707
Get it?

751
01:03:47,791 --> 01:03:48,332
Leave!

752
01:03:51,499 --> 01:03:52,666
What are you doing?

753
01:03:53,499 --> 01:03:55,249
What does their past have to do with us?

754
01:03:55,291 --> 01:03:56,041
Shut up.

755
01:03:56,499 --> 01:03:57,541
Don't get my boss in trouble.

756
01:03:57,624 --> 01:03:58,082
Leave!

757
01:04:19,874 --> 01:04:21,749
Do you want to kick me out, too?

758
01:04:23,207 --> 01:04:25,124
I'm the man who killed your father.

759
01:04:26,582 --> 01:04:28,124
I don't know him.

760
01:04:28,457 --> 01:04:29,957
What he did is none of my business.

761
01:04:32,457 --> 01:04:33,416
Leave.

762
01:04:34,916 --> 01:04:37,541
I once thought I had nothing.

763
01:04:38,916 --> 01:04:40,624
You were the only one who fed me

764
01:04:40,666 --> 01:04:41,582
and took me in.

765
01:04:43,541 --> 01:04:44,666
I'm not leaving!

766
01:04:53,082 --> 01:04:54,749
You have no choice.

767
01:04:56,291 --> 01:04:56,874
Leave!

768
01:04:57,166 --> 01:04:58,624
Leave!

769
01:05:27,207 --> 01:05:29,249
Why didn't you tell me yesterday?

770
01:05:30,291 --> 01:05:31,832
He owes me three lives.

771
01:05:32,749 --> 01:05:34,082
I've waited years for this.

772
01:05:34,541 --> 01:05:36,124
I'm claiming him now.

773
01:05:36,832 --> 01:05:37,582
Simple question:

774
01:05:38,582 --> 01:05:40,082
Yes or no?

775
01:05:42,416 --> 01:05:43,249
Get him!

776
01:06:35,874 --> 01:06:37,332
- Slaughter him!
- Over there!

777
01:06:38,416 --> 01:06:39,416
Stop him!

778
01:08:43,749 --> 01:08:44,832
Son of a bitch!

779
01:09:31,374 --> 01:09:32,874
Another step closer...

780
01:09:33,249 --> 01:09:34,832
And I'll kill you.

781
01:09:42,624 --> 01:09:44,457
Your father's debt...

782
01:09:46,041 --> 01:09:48,207
Will take you lifetimes to pay.

783
01:10:09,749 --> 01:10:10,791
Kill him!

784
01:10:17,874 --> 01:10:19,666
Don't come back to Hong Kong.

785
01:10:26,999 --> 01:10:27,832
Don't you leave!

786
01:10:31,374 --> 01:10:32,249
Boss.

787
01:10:56,207 --> 01:10:57,082
Stop!

788
01:11:13,999 --> 01:11:15,541
What's passed is past.

789
01:11:17,124 --> 01:11:18,207
Leave it there.

790
01:11:20,457 --> 01:11:22,082
Like hell I will!

791
01:11:38,541 --> 01:11:39,624
Boss.

792
01:12:05,832 --> 01:12:07,499
All bets are off!

793
01:12:07,499 --> 01:12:08,207
What a hand!

794
01:12:16,457 --> 01:12:17,582
Where's Mr. Big?

795
01:12:18,249 --> 01:12:19,582
He's taking a nap.

796
01:12:19,666 --> 01:12:21,041
You can talk to me.

797
01:12:21,499 --> 01:12:22,457
I'll wait for him.

798
01:12:28,124 --> 01:12:30,291
I end up doing the work anyway.

799
01:12:40,874 --> 01:12:42,374
I want Chan Lok-kwun dead.

800
01:12:46,124 --> 01:12:47,499
It'll cost you.

801
01:12:47,707 --> 01:12:49,749
I'll pay whatever you want.

802
01:12:53,499 --> 01:12:55,582
I'll have to go into the Walled City.

803
01:13:10,791 --> 01:13:12,416
Go ahead, sit.

804
01:13:23,916 --> 01:13:25,291
Since you've come to me,

805
01:13:25,374 --> 01:13:27,541
that means you've fallen out with Cyclone.

806
01:13:27,749 --> 01:13:29,749
Can I take his place, then?

807
01:13:31,249 --> 01:13:33,249
As long as you kill Chan Lok-Kwun...

808
01:13:34,124 --> 01:13:35,541
I'll give you whatever you want.

809
01:13:36,707 --> 01:13:37,916
Deal.

810
01:13:55,124 --> 01:13:56,207
How is he?

811
01:13:56,291 --> 01:13:57,249
I stopped his bleeding.

812
01:13:57,291 --> 01:13:58,749
His internal organs are hurt.

813
01:13:59,041 --> 01:14:00,749
Chau won't give up so easily.

814
01:14:01,332 --> 01:14:02,999
We have to get him out.

815
01:14:03,457 --> 01:14:04,916
Will it be dangerous to move him?

816
01:14:05,582 --> 01:14:07,082
It'll be more dangerous if he stays.

817
01:14:08,457 --> 01:14:09,291
All right.

818
01:14:12,207 --> 01:14:13,416
Make the arrangements.

819
01:14:32,041 --> 01:14:33,457
You're very sick.

820
01:14:34,541 --> 01:14:36,166
You need the hospital.

821
01:14:39,999 --> 01:14:41,374
I'm fine.

822
01:15:13,124 --> 01:15:14,374
Mr. Big has come in.

823
01:15:14,457 --> 01:15:15,707
He's looking for Lok.

824
01:15:16,166 --> 01:15:16,999
Boss.

825
01:15:17,457 --> 01:15:18,749
You leave with Lok.

826
01:15:18,832 --> 01:15:20,291
I'll handle Mr. Big.

827
01:15:46,999 --> 01:15:48,166
I'm counting on you.

828
01:15:54,374 --> 01:15:55,499
Shin.

829
01:15:56,624 --> 01:15:57,916
Watch your boss's back.

830
01:16:03,582 --> 01:16:05,124
Get to work!

831
01:16:05,916 --> 01:16:07,332
Scram!

832
01:16:07,457 --> 01:16:09,082
Have you seen him?

833
01:16:09,082 --> 01:16:10,416
Have you seen this guy?

834
01:16:10,541 --> 01:16:11,666
Look closer.

835
01:16:11,707 --> 01:16:13,832
Have you seen this guy? Chan Lok-kwun!

836
01:16:13,832 --> 01:16:15,166
Never seen him!

837
01:16:16,249 --> 01:16:17,416
Have you seen him?

838
01:16:17,791 --> 01:16:19,666
No? Are you sure?!

839
01:16:21,082 --> 01:16:22,291
Messages for 3323?

840
01:16:30,207 --> 01:16:31,332
What's up?

841
01:16:34,457 --> 01:16:35,999
Mr. Big's entered the Walled City.

842
01:16:36,749 --> 01:16:38,124
Boss Chau's not letting Lok go.

843
01:16:42,332 --> 01:16:43,541
I have to go back in.

844
01:16:43,832 --> 01:16:45,791
When I was 13, I almost OD'd in there.

845
01:16:45,874 --> 01:16:47,957
I'm here today because Cyclone saved me.

846
01:16:48,332 --> 01:16:50,582
He's going to save Lok like he saved me.

847
01:16:50,832 --> 01:16:51,957
I won't abandon them!

848
01:16:51,999 --> 01:16:53,207
I won't abandon the Walled City!

849
01:17:00,291 --> 01:17:01,457
I get it.

850
01:17:02,416 --> 01:17:03,957
Watch your back.

851
01:17:05,166 --> 01:17:07,291
You still have to watch mine.

852
01:17:08,124 --> 01:17:09,916
I knew I'm with the right boss.

853
01:17:13,832 --> 01:17:14,624
Go back!

854
01:17:14,999 --> 01:17:16,082
AV will get Lok out.

855
01:17:16,082 --> 01:17:17,499
I'll go with you.

856
01:17:21,499 --> 01:17:23,082
You said you're counting on me!

857
